<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4658266>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Allopauropus (D.) crassescens sp. n. (a–d, f–h) Holotype female; (e) paratype male; (i) paratype female. (a) Head, right side, dorsal view; (b) pygidium, dorsal view; (c) left antenna, dorsal view; (d) collum segment, median part, ventral view; (e) genital papillae; (f) tarsus of leg 9; (g) seta on coxa of leg 9; (h) seta on trochanter of leg 9; (i) T3." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4658266/files/figure.png" .

